                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre but careful.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red.</seg>
                        <date>20th century.</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names; names of the donors; incipit of Text
                           I; titles of books to be read; initial line of the readings; the word
                           bārǝkanna… “bless us…” in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals. 
 On the incipit pages of Text I
                           (fols.4r), a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black
                           lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
